<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="000_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯嗯，<delay20 />是想要拍结婚纪念照片啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拍摄的话，<delay8 />用我的摄影棚，
也是可以的哦<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="000_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
拍摄场景<delay8 />要怎么布置才好呢，<delay40 />
我们要做准备的话，<delay8 />感觉有点困难<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />！
你来啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我有点事情想拜托你<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_00" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />！
你来得正是时候呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我有点事情想拜托你<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00">这位<colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />，</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是一对恩爱夫妻哦，<delay40 />
他们想要拍摄结婚纪念照。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道，说到6月，就会想到六月新娘嘛！<delay20 />
所以每年到了这个时候，<delay8 />
他们都会拍照留念哦。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="01 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是有一个问题<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />地方可以借用我的摄影棚，<delay20 />
但却没有人帮忙搭建重要的场景。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以！<delay20 />想请你帮忙搭建
婚礼摄影的场景哦！<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想请你做的事情，<delay20 />
就是把婚礼摄影场景中所必需的家具<delay20 />
摆放在适合拍进照片中的位置。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />场景中所使用的的家具<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会由我这边准备，<delay8 />所以请放心！<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />大概就是这么回事，<delay20 />
怎么样？<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你愿意吗？</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />交给我吧！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真没办法啊</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗？！<delay20 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会感谢你这份情的！<10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就早点开始做准备吧！<delay20 />
来，快进<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />摄影棚吧！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里就是婚礼摄影专用的摄影棚啦！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="4" />虽然只是更换了<delay8 />
里面房间的壁纸和地板……<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是第一次使用摄影棚吧。<delay20 />
我来简单说明一下使用方法。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要更改摄影棚的场景时，<delay20 />
使用<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />按照自己房子的感觉<delay20 />
自由地更改布置吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用来装饰场景的<delay8 />
家具和杂货等，<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是和<colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />
签订了租借协议的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以只要是刊登在
<tag a="110" b="1" /><colour id="1" />目录<colour id="65535" />中的物品，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都可以立即拿来装饰！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />使用方法和平时的摄影棚一样，放心吧。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前已经和<tag a="110" b="1" />说明过了，<delay8 />
这次就省略了哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你忘记了，<delay20 />
我反正就在外面，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以随时来问我。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，对了对了！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />中途离开房间也没关系，<delay20 />
继续的时候跟我说一声就行。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />至于具体要做什么，<delay8 />
详细情况可以问<colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />。<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay8 />就拜托你了哦！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呀，<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
你来了啊！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="04 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是来帮忙给<colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
拍摄婚礼照片的吗？<delay40 />
还是说<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要询问关于摄影棚的事？</message>
	<message label="010_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">帮忙拍摄婚礼照片</message>
	<message label="010_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">关于摄影棚</message>
	<message label="010_c" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没什么事</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦！谢谢！<delay20 />
是来帮忙拍摄婚礼照片的啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay8 />我去准备下，<delay8 />稍等。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="08 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想问关于什么呢？</message>
	<message label="012_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">关于场景</message>
	<message label="012_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">关于模特</message>
	<message label="012_c" attrib="00 00 00 00">关于服装</message>
	<message label="012_d" attrib="00 00 00 00">关于拍摄</message>
	<message label="012_e" attrib="00 00 00 00">不用了</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想使用摄影棚的话，<delay20 />
可以随意使用，没关系哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想拍摄<colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />的
婚礼照片的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就来跟我说吧。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦！<delay8 />辛苦了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来顺利拍好照片了呢。</message>
	<message label="014_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以的话，<delay20 />
明天也想请你来帮忙哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，<delay8 />那就拜托你了哦！</message>
	<message label="014_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天六月就要结束了。<delay20 />
听说他们两位明天也要回去了哦。<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉变得有点冷清了呢。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay8 />超级棒的派对呢！<delay frames="40" />
我借出自己的摄影棚
真的很值得啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拜托你真是太正确了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的谢谢你！</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！辛苦了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经是<delay8 />场景制作的专家了呢。<delay8 />
哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="017_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感谢你的帮忙！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小小心意，<delay8 />不成敬意！</message>
	<message label="017_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就请收下吧！<delay20 />
是<colour id="1" />婚礼栅栏<colour id="65535" />的DIY手册！</message>
	<message label="017_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我是想给你的，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你的包包已满，<delay8 />我给不了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请整理好持有物以后，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再跟我说一声，我再给你吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之，<delay8 />我对你真是感激不尽！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欢迎你随时再来玩！</message>
	<message label="017_04" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
你是来拿<delay8 />刚才没能给你的礼物啊！<10_4 />
是<colour id="1" />婚礼栅栏<colour id="65535" />的DIY手册！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />我也想像健兆那样，<delay8 />
轻轻松松<delay8 />就能制作出来，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但果然还是太难了啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你这么能干，肯定行的！<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要做做看哦！</message>
	<message label="018_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你说什么？<delay20 />
你也不会<colour id="1" />DIY<colour id="65535" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
这就麻烦了啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />对了！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我听说可以去试试<delay8 />
<colour id="1" />DIY工坊<colour id="65535" />这个东西哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要去<colour id="1" />服务处<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
找<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />谈谈呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是个好机会，<delay8 />
我也可以学学呢。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="04 00 00 00">对了，<delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天你也是来帮忙给<colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
拍摄婚礼照片的吗？<delay40 />
还是说<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要询问关于摄影棚的事？</message>
	<message label="019_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">帮忙拍摄婚礼照片</message>
	<message label="019_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">关于摄影棚</message>
	<message label="019_c" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没什么事</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀呀，<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很感谢你<delay8 />
上个月帮忙制作婚礼的拍摄场景呢！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
心满意足地回去了哦。<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这多亏了你呢！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />回去了。<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他们很高兴，<delay8 />
还说“能拍到好照片真是太棒了”。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />莉咏<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />已经回去了，<delay20 />
