	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
恩爱的夫妻，<delay8 />真是不错呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
